title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 62] Post-Punk, Gothic
description:
It's been a while since I posted vol. 61 of these series, but I just don't post music for the sake of posting only. I have gone over my music archive recently, listened to some great stuff and came up with these records for you to download and enjoy. Please do not forget to seed. Imagine a year from now someone might have any of these on his/her wish list. 



Music For Pleasure - Blacklands [1985]

Red Temple Spirits - Dancing to Restore an Eclipsed Moon [1988]

The Bizarre Orkeztra - A Beautiful Place [1987]

The Blitz - Second Empire Justice [1983]
